<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .error-container {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8d7da 0%, #f5c6cb 100%);
            border: 2px solid #dc3545;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .error-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #dc3545;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .attempt-counter {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .progress-bar {
            width: 100%;
            height: 20px;
            background: #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .progress-fill {
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #dc3545, #c82333);
            width: <%= (attempt / maxAttempts) * 100 %>%;
            transition: width 0.3s ease;
        }
        .retry-info {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #856404;
        }
        .error-details {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: white;
            background: #dc3545;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="error-icon">üîÑ‚ùå</div>
        <h1><%= title %></h1>
        <p>This request failed as part of the flaky endpoint testing. It will succeed after <%= maxAttempts %> failed attempts.</p>
        
        <div class="attempt-counter">
            <h3>Attempt Progress</h3>
            <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                <span><strong>Current Attempt:</strong> <%= attempt %> of <%= maxAttempts %></span>
                <span class="status-badge">FAILED</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="progress-bar">
                <div class="progress-fill"></div>
            </div>
            
            <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;">
                <% if (willSucceed) { %>
                    ‚úÖ <strong>Next attempt will succeed!</strong>
                <% } else { %>
                    ‚è≥ <%= maxAttempts - attempt %> more failures expected
                <% } %>
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="error-details">
            <h3>Error Information</h3>
            <p><strong>Status:</strong> <%= errorStatus %> - <%= errorMessage %></p>
            <p><strong>Attempt:</strong> <%= attempt %> / <%= maxAttempts %></p>
            <p><strong>Will Succeed:</strong> <%= willSucceed ? 'Yes (next attempt)' : 'No (more failures needed)' %></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="retry-info">
            <h4>üîÑ Retry Testing</h4>
            <p>This endpoint is designed to test retry logic in HTTP clients and CLI tools:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>First <%= maxAttempts %> requests will fail with different error codes</li>
                <li>Request <%= maxAttempts + 1 %> and beyond will succeed</li>
                <li>Each client (IP + User-Agent) has its own failure counter</li>
                <li>Use this to test exponential backoff and retry strategies</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div style="background: #e7f3ff; border: 1px solid #b3d9ff; border-radius: 4px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <h4>CLI Testing</h4>
            <p><strong>Test retry behavior with:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li><code>--retry-attempts 3</code> - Set number of retry attempts</li>
                <li><code>--retry-delay 1000</code> - Set delay between retries</li>
                <li><code>--continue-on-error</code> - Continue batch processing on errors</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p><strong>Expected behavior:</strong> CLI should retry this request and eventually succeed.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>